column5: Went out fishing on the big O last night for a couple of hours, and managed to snag two decent muskie, a 43" and a 50". Here is a pic of the 50" that my buddy snagged. Beauty fish. Bent out a 5/0 mustad hook! What a fight.  Have to give a shout out to Mr. Marc Thorpe for showing me the way of the ROMO. Caught the 43" on a romotail. HAHA!    Patowski
Nice first post Dude. Sweet musky too.
WOW!! Nice ski!!  Also, welcome to the board...hope to see many more pics and reports like this one!!
Great Fish!!! One of these days Im going to have to hit that place up for a week.
Dang...welcome to the board...dang nice ski
Wow, thats an impressive brute.  Nothing like fish porn for your first post  Now I gotta go google romotails!
Nice fish, great report, welcome to OFC Hawgwob...I mean Patow!
Good to see MILF is still alive!
